Class Character

  • java.lang.Object
    • Character

  • public class Character
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is part of the "The Chase" application. "The Chase" is an extremely complicated, text based adventure game. This class defines the characters that one are able to interact with throughout the course of the game.
    Version:
    2013.12.19
    Author:
    Viktor Holmér
